synchronization:
is the process by which we control the accessability of multiple threads to a particular shared resource

without syncronization :data inconsistancy ,thread interference

## Thread Class Constructors (8)

```java
Thread()

Thread(Runnable target)

Thread(String name)

Thread(Runnable target, String name)

Thread(ThreadGroup tg, Runnable target)

Thread(ThreadGroup tg, String name)

Thread(ThreadGroup tg, Runnable target, String name)

Thread(ThreadGroup tg, Runnable target, String name, long stackSize)
```

